  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "quadratic-residue",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/quadratic-residue/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.04,
      "size": 32688,
      "text": "普通的平方我们很熟悉，一四九十六，都是完全平方数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "quadratic-residue",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/quadratic-residue/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32256,
      "text": "可是在时钟一样的模运算里，哪些数才算得上是平方数呢？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "quadratic-residue",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/quadratic-residue/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.51,
      "size": 40176,
      "text": "比如模七的世界里，把一到六各自平方再取余，结果只落在几个数上。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "quadratic-residue",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "define-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/quadratic-residue/xiaoxiao/define-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.46,
      "size": 39312,
      "text": "如果方程 x 的平方同余 a 模 p 有解，就称 a 是模 p 的二次剩余。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "quadratic-residue",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "define-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/quadratic-residue/xiaoxiao/define-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.63,
      "size": 26064,
      "text": "换句话说，a 是模 p 世界里的一个完全平方。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "quadratic-residue",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "define-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/quadratic-residue/xiaoxiao/define-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.69,
      "size": 43056,
      "text": "对奇素数 p，非零的二次剩余恰好有 (p 减一) 除以二 个，正好一半。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "quadratic-residue",
      "section_id": "legendre",
      "line_id": "leg-1",
      "filename": "legendre-leg-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/quadratic-residue/xiaoxiao/legendre-leg-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.69,
      "size": 27072,
      "text": "数学家用勒让德符号 a 比 p 来记录这件事。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "quadratic-residue",
      "section_id": "legendre",
      "line_id": "leg-2",
      "filename": "legendre-leg-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/quadratic-residue/xiaoxiao/legendre-leg-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.39,
      "size": 38304,
      "text": "它等于一表示 a 是剩余，等于负一表示不是，等于零表示 p 整除 a。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "quadratic-residue",
      "section_id": "euler",
      "line_id": "eul-1",
      "filename": "euler-eul-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/quadratic-residue/xiaoxiao/euler-eul-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.54,
      "size": 40608,
      "text": "欧拉给出一个漂亮的判据：算 a 的 (p 减一) 除以二 次方，再模 p。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "quadratic-residue",
      "section_id": "euler",
      "line_id": "eul-2",
      "filename": "euler-eul-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/quadratic-residue/xiaoxiao/euler-eul-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.63,
      "size": 42048,
      "text": "结果是一，a 就是二次剩余；结果是 p 减一，也就是负一，它就不是。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "quadratic-residue",
      "section_id": "euler",
      "line_id": "eul-3",
      "filename": "euler-eul-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/quadratic-residue/xiaoxiao/euler-eul-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.49,
      "size": 23760,
      "text": "一次快速幂取模，就能判断任意一个数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "quadratic-residue",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/quadratic-residue/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.1,
      "size": 33552,
      "text": "切换不同的素数 p，看绿色的剩余点在圆环上如何分布。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "quadratic-residue",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/quadratic-residue/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.52,
      "size": 40320,
      "text": "注意 x 和 p 减 x 的连线，它们总是落到同一个剩余上，对称又优雅。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "quadratic-residue",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/quadratic-residue/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.55,
      "size": 24768,
      "text": "二次剩余就是模 p 世界里的完全平方数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "quadratic-residue",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/quadratic-residue/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35280,
      "text": "勒让德符号记录归属，欧拉判别法用快速幂高效判定。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "quadratic-residue",
